sources.title: Eagle And The Albatross | Full Movie | Comedy Drama | Amber Liu
sources.description:
Eagle And The Albatross - An uprooted teen (Amber Liu) whose #1 passion is golf, serendipitously moves in with her aunt (who runs a golf course), where she confronts her grief and fears, under the unlikely mentorship of a stubborn local golf legend (Dan Lauria).
2020.  Stars: Adrienne Barbeau, Michael Badalucco, Dan Lauria, Amber Liu

metadata.Plot: When an orphaned half Korean girl finds herself in small town America with her only living relative, she seeks out a mentor to help with the only things she loves - golf. The best player in town, the widowed optometrist, takes her under his wing, sending them on a journey to face their fear of losing loved ones and their game. The only problem is, he has three months to live.
metadata.Actors: Adrienne Barbeau, Dan Lauria, Jay Huguley
